WEBVTT

00:14.000 --> 00:16.730
If Xie Jiayu knew you were
going to harm her today,

00:17.000 --> 00:18.660
I wonder what she would think.

00:19.190 --> 00:20.440
Believe it or not,

00:21.480 --> 00:23.280
thank you for stopping me today.

00:24.070 --> 00:25.400
I didn't want to do this.

00:26.600 --> 00:27.800
Tonight is eventful.

00:28.070 --> 00:30.760
You should return to the palace early,
Your Highness.

00:30.760 --> 00:31.690
Young Lord Xiao.

00:32.560 --> 00:33.960
Are you really confident

00:34.540 --> 00:36.940
that you can protect them
both in Jiankang?

00:37.160 --> 00:38.710
When winter comes and the grass withers,

00:38.710 --> 00:40.880
the Northern Qin's forces
will definitely come south again.

00:40.880 --> 00:43.880
You and the Beifu soldiers
will leave sooner or later.

00:48.390 --> 00:49.520
My brother once said

00:50.110 --> 00:52.960
that his best friend is an ambitious man,

00:53.280 --> 00:54.410
whose lifelong wish

00:54.470 --> 00:57.330
is to become the most powerful general
in the world.

00:58.430 --> 01:00.030
You have indeed achieved it.

01:01.070 --> 01:02.130
But Your Highness,

01:02.390 --> 01:04.450
the most powerful person in the world

01:05.790 --> 01:06.790
is the emperor.

01:08.510 --> 01:10.000
For power,

01:10.950 --> 01:12.120
will you really

01:12.840 --> 01:14.900
cross swords with my brother one day?

01:17.150 --> 01:18.680
According to what you said,

01:19.200 --> 01:20.070
it seems you are very certain

01:20.070 --> 01:22.200
that your brother will stay in the palace.

01:22.200 --> 01:23.150
We both know

01:23.640 --> 01:26.900
that from the day my brother
stepped into Jiankang Palace,

01:27.150 --> 01:28.480
it has become a dead end.

01:29.950 --> 01:32.039
Even if the Empress Dowager
has much dissatisfaction,

01:32.039 --> 01:33.070
she also knows

01:33.590 --> 01:36.050
no one is a better candidate
than my brother.

01:36.560 --> 01:38.890
You brought Jiayu to see my brother today.

01:39.039 --> 01:40.759
Although out of good intentions,

01:40.759 --> 01:42.490
it's just a short-sighted fix.

01:43.870 --> 01:45.400
Don't you want your brother

01:45.680 --> 01:47.140
to be with the one he loves?

01:49.680 --> 01:51.350
My brother has no way out.

01:53.070 --> 01:53.800
As for Jiayu,

01:54.479 --> 01:56.280
she should be an eagle in the sky.

01:56.870 --> 01:59.479
She doesn't want to be bound
by these palace walls.

01:59.479 --> 02:00.710
As Jiayu's friend,

02:02.120 --> 02:04.380
I also don't want her to enter the palace.

02:12.120 --> 02:13.080
You go back to the palace first.

02:13.080 --> 02:14.100
As long as you don't show up tonight,

02:14.100 --> 02:16.630
I promise your brother
and Jiayu will be fine.

03:47.970 --> 03:51.880
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

03:52.340 --> 03:54.790
[Episode 7]

03:58.630 --> 03:59.240
Mao.

04:00.750 --> 04:03.150
How much longer
will you stay in the palace?

04:03.630 --> 04:05.560
Don't you like me being the Regent?

04:08.910 --> 04:09.770
I don't like it.

04:10.190 --> 04:11.390
It feels very distant

04:11.870 --> 04:12.800
and unfamiliar.

04:15.470 --> 04:16.260
They say

04:16.800 --> 04:19.329
the Regent will become
the Crown Prince next.

04:21.190 --> 04:22.590
I haven't become one yet.

04:23.190 --> 04:25.870
Besides, the Empress Dowager
doesn't want me to either.

04:25.870 --> 04:26.310
Mao.

04:27.560 --> 04:29.560
Are you still willing to leave with me?

04:29.560 --> 04:30.160
Of course.

04:30.880 --> 04:33.480
I just want to be with the person
I like the most.

04:36.310 --> 04:36.909
Excuse me.

04:37.159 --> 04:38.159
Careful, Yaoyao.

04:43.510 --> 04:45.470
It's the fake Xiao Sheng
who bought the repeating crossbow.

04:45.470 --> 04:46.310
It's that swindler!

04:46.310 --> 04:46.800
Yaoyao!

04:48.480 --> 04:49.480
Stop right there!

04:50.159 --> 04:51.960
Tonight, the Empress Dowager will use
the Young Master of Miraculous Craft

04:51.960 --> 04:53.680
to cause a mutiny
among the Beifu soldiers.

04:53.680 --> 04:55.730
Don't let Xie Jiayu
get near the Monument of Loyalty.

04:55.730 --> 04:57.140
Don't let her get involved.

04:57.140 --> 04:57.630
Yaoyao!

05:17.000 --> 05:17.830
Liu Yu'e.

05:20.240 --> 05:21.000
Madam Liu.

05:23.040 --> 05:24.430
Greetings, Your Highness.

05:24.430 --> 05:26.950
What are you doing
at the Double Ninth Ceremony?

05:26.950 --> 05:28.040
The Empress Dowager
has made a move tonight.

05:28.040 --> 05:29.970
Tell your people to leave quickly.

05:34.560 --> 05:35.290
Who's there?

05:40.310 --> 05:42.390
I trust you've fared well,
Young Lord Xiao.

05:42.390 --> 05:43.450
Or I should call you

05:43.870 --> 05:45.159
Crown Prince Wenxi.

05:49.240 --> 05:50.950
Your Highness,
with the Phoenix Heart Token,

05:50.950 --> 05:52.630
you haven't appeared for over 20 years.

05:52.630 --> 05:54.490
Since you suddenly appear today,

05:54.560 --> 05:55.620
what are you after?

05:56.000 --> 05:58.000
I did have another purpose at first.

05:58.900 --> 06:01.340
But now I will use the Phoenix Heart Token

06:02.390 --> 06:03.450
to set Yaoyao free.

06:04.270 --> 06:05.190
What do you mean?

06:05.190 --> 06:06.990
I want you to pick a suitable time

06:07.600 --> 06:08.600
to divorce Yaoyao

06:09.240 --> 06:10.900
and allow her to marry freely.

06:16.040 --> 06:18.300
Although I don't like being threatened,

06:18.680 --> 06:19.800
it's not difficult to do what you said.

06:19.800 --> 06:20.800
I'm not finished.

06:21.720 --> 06:23.780
Prince Qi is not suitable for Yaoyao.

06:24.080 --> 06:25.410
I want them to separate.

06:25.790 --> 06:27.790
If you can help me do this,

06:28.800 --> 06:31.430
I will be at your disposal, Your Highness.

06:37.000 --> 06:37.560
Halt!

06:37.880 --> 06:38.880
Yaoyao, don't go!

06:39.800 --> 06:40.950
His Highness has ordered

06:40.950 --> 06:42.140
that you can't approach
the Monument of Loyalty.

06:42.140 --> 06:44.040
That is the fake Xiao Sheng
who bought the repeating crossbow!

06:44.040 --> 06:44.630
What?

06:45.720 --> 06:46.270
He's still alive?

06:46.270 --> 06:47.600
It's too late. Let's go!

06:47.800 --> 06:48.260
Yaoyao!

06:48.720 --> 06:49.360
Great!

06:49.680 --> 06:50.280
Excuse me.

06:50.920 --> 06:52.750
Bright silver gold-painted spear,

06:52.750 --> 06:54.140
weighing 24 jin,

06:54.600 --> 06:56.330
offered to General Zhang Zuwu.

06:57.000 --> 06:57.950
Armor-breaking blade,

06:57.950 --> 06:59.070
weighing 48 jin,

06:59.680 --> 07:01.480
offered to General Li Wenzhong.

07:02.430 --> 07:04.030
To the heroic spirits above,

07:04.040 --> 07:07.170
the Young Master of Miraculous Craft
sends his regards.

07:09.310 --> 07:10.360
It's done, Your Majesty.

07:10.360 --> 07:11.960
Xie Jiayu has taken the bait.

07:12.000 --> 07:13.720
Keeping Hong Qi alive is indeed useful.

07:13.720 --> 07:15.580
You really have great foresight.

07:19.550 --> 07:22.280
Look at how exquisitely
this lantern is painted.

07:30.520 --> 07:31.920
I don't like it.

07:35.000 --> 07:36.860
Look over there. Why is it on fire?

07:38.920 --> 07:41.310
The Young Master of Miraculous Craft
actually burned the offerings!

07:41.310 --> 07:43.700
Burned
by the Young Master of Miraculous Craft.

07:43.700 --> 07:45.340
[Dead]

07:46.190 --> 07:49.600
30,000 loyal souls
return to their homeland.

07:53.730 --> 07:55.450
Seeing today's scene,

07:56.560 --> 07:58.690
I wonder what these 30,000 loyal souls

07:59.510 --> 08:00.600
would think.

08:04.120 --> 08:05.630
Beifu Army, listen to my orders!

08:05.630 --> 08:06.290
-Yes!
-Yes!

08:07.360 --> 08:08.420
Surround the altar

08:08.430 --> 08:11.030
and find
the Young Master of Miraculous Craft.

08:13.560 --> 08:15.170
The Beifu Army is killing people!

08:15.170 --> 08:17.030
The Beifu Army is killing people!

08:23.190 --> 08:24.360
-Murder!
-Stop!

08:24.890 --> 08:25.720
Stop!

08:25.830 --> 08:26.690
Hurry up and go!

08:26.870 --> 08:28.130
Beifu Army, listen up!

08:28.600 --> 08:30.060
Do not harm the civilians!

08:30.720 --> 08:31.390
Stop!

08:38.789 --> 08:39.960
Your Highness, what took you so long?

08:39.960 --> 08:41.480
I was delayed by something.

08:41.480 --> 08:42.630
Has everything been arranged?

08:42.630 --> 08:44.790
I didn't expect it
to really be Fang Shiba and Lu Dayong.

08:44.790 --> 08:46.320
Last time you whipped them,

08:46.630 --> 08:47.690
they must have held a grudge.

08:47.690 --> 08:48.960
They were bought off
by the Empress Dowager

08:48.960 --> 08:50.820
to incite the soldiers to mutiny.

08:51.910 --> 08:52.390
Do it.

08:52.550 --> 08:53.080
Yes.

08:56.050 --> 08:56.530
Wait.

08:57.840 --> 08:59.240
Why is Xie Jiayu here too?

09:00.600 --> 09:01.460
Your Highness.

09:01.480 --> 09:02.940
Do not harm the civilians!

09:12.470 --> 09:13.630
The Monument of Loyalty is about to fall!

09:13.630 --> 09:14.710
Everyone, run!

09:16.480 --> 09:17.240
Run!

09:18.120 --> 09:20.920
Yan Yue, quickly direct
the civilians to run east.

09:24.960 --> 09:25.550
Run!

09:25.550 --> 09:26.480
Yao, run now!

09:33.080 --> 09:35.810
I don't know
if this Soul-Chasing Bomb will work.

09:53.750 --> 09:54.950
Are you alright, Yao?

10:00.030 --> 10:00.960
It's dangerous here.

10:00.960 --> 10:01.750
What are you doing here?

10:01.750 --> 10:02.670
To save you.

10:03.240 --> 10:04.600
If my Soul-Chasing Bomb hadn't worked

10:04.600 --> 10:06.080
and shattered the Monument of Loyalty,

10:06.080 --> 10:06.870
and if it had fallen directly on you,

10:06.870 --> 10:07.870
you'd be dead now.

10:29.210 --> 10:31.120
Yao, you're not hurt, are you?

10:32.270 --> 10:32.800
I'm fine.

10:35.630 --> 10:37.190
Let Qing Long take you back first.

10:37.190 --> 10:37.590
Yes.

10:47.360 --> 10:48.910
She is Xie Jiayu.

10:51.630 --> 10:54.090
She is
the Young Master of Miraculous Craft.

10:55.200 --> 10:56.120
She

10:56.790 --> 10:58.590
blew up the Monument of Loyalty.

10:59.320 --> 11:00.510
Stop making false accusations.

11:00.510 --> 11:01.510
I blew up the monument

11:01.510 --> 11:02.670
just now to save people.

11:02.670 --> 11:04.240
Besides, it was about to fall anyway.

11:04.240 --> 11:05.150
Stop arguing.

11:05.840 --> 11:08.700
The monument was perfectly fine.
How could it fall?

11:08.790 --> 11:09.950
If not you,

11:10.600 --> 11:12.660
then the wrath of 30,000 loyal souls.

11:14.270 --> 11:15.480
All because of you,

11:16.230 --> 11:18.760
so many of our men
died in the Northern Border.

11:19.970 --> 11:21.090
I will kill you

11:21.870 --> 11:23.200
to avenge our brothers!

11:28.390 --> 11:30.600
Your Highness, if you protect her,

11:31.000 --> 11:33.860
you are not fit to be the commander
of the Beifu Army!

11:42.720 --> 11:43.550
Fire!

11:43.970 --> 11:44.980
Fire!

11:49.820 --> 11:50.350
Let's go.

11:58.790 --> 12:01.830
His Highness is determined
to protect the culprit.

12:04.960 --> 12:06.440
Are we just going to endure this?

12:06.440 --> 12:08.440
I'm in for what you suggested.

12:09.490 --> 12:10.350
Your Highness.

12:12.270 --> 12:13.870
Are you still going after her?

12:13.870 --> 12:16.060
Tonight, Her Majesty and His Highness
will surely have a showdown.

12:16.060 --> 12:17.860
You can't get involved anymore.

12:18.790 --> 12:19.440
But Yaoyao...

12:19.440 --> 12:22.200
His Highness
won't let anything happen to her.

12:24.200 --> 12:25.330
It's time to go back.

12:30.330 --> 12:33.300
[Hong Qi]

12:30.720 --> 12:33.250
Thank you, Your Majesty,
for sparing my life.

12:34.840 --> 12:36.360
I spared your life today.

12:37.560 --> 12:38.440
From now on,

12:39.160 --> 12:41.560
you shall no longer exist
in Jiankang City.

12:42.030 --> 12:43.630
Rest assured, Your Majesty.

12:44.910 --> 12:46.240
Ready to move.

13:11.240 --> 13:12.960
-Who allowed you to go to the altar?
-Who told you to hug me?

13:12.960 --> 13:15.420
-I did it to save you.
-I did it to save people.

13:23.800 --> 13:25.890
I think you're going to lose to me.

13:29.630 --> 13:30.160
Let's go.

13:31.910 --> 13:33.080
When I say you're foolish,

13:33.080 --> 13:34.390
you really don't use your brain.

13:34.390 --> 13:36.150
We agreed that you would
only be Qing Long tonight.

13:36.150 --> 13:37.030
Qing Long?

13:37.550 --> 13:40.540
Would you arrange for Qing Long
and Mao to meet and view lanterns?

13:40.540 --> 13:42.670
I shouldn't have arranged
for you two to meet.

13:42.670 --> 13:44.080
What? Are you envious?

13:44.440 --> 13:45.370
Are you jealous?

13:45.790 --> 13:46.720
Even if you are,

13:47.160 --> 13:48.300
Mao only wants to see me,

13:48.300 --> 13:48.940
not you.

13:52.720 --> 13:54.670
Don't think
I haven't seen right through you.

13:54.670 --> 13:56.080
The Empress Dowager making trouble today

13:56.080 --> 13:58.010
was all within your expectations.

13:58.150 --> 13:59.550
The Empress Dowager used me.

13:59.550 --> 14:00.410
Father used me.

14:00.960 --> 14:02.360
Aren't you using me too?

14:05.510 --> 14:06.710
Make yourself clear.

14:07.720 --> 14:09.120
When have I ever used you?

14:09.140 --> 14:11.270
You had already arranged
your men for tonight, right?

14:11.270 --> 14:13.550
The Empress Dowager intentionally
tampered with the Monument of Loyalty

14:13.550 --> 14:14.600
and used
the Young Master of Miraculous Craft

14:14.600 --> 14:16.710
to sow discord
between you and the Beifu soldiers.

14:16.710 --> 14:18.170
And you just played along.

14:18.320 --> 14:19.320
The paper weapons

14:19.600 --> 14:21.480
and those indignant Beifu soldiers—

14:21.480 --> 14:23.340
weren't they all prepared by you?

14:23.600 --> 14:24.870
You played along with her tricks,

14:24.870 --> 14:27.120
making the Empress Dowager think
she had won a total victory tonight.

14:27.120 --> 14:28.200
By making a risky move,

14:28.200 --> 14:30.530
you could completely grasp her weakness.

14:30.870 --> 14:32.270
Anyway, you just used me.

14:32.670 --> 14:33.800
I went up to the altar

14:33.870 --> 14:35.150
and became a target of public criticism.

14:35.150 --> 14:36.080
Didn't it help you make this play

14:36.080 --> 14:37.280
look more realistic?

14:38.480 --> 14:40.600
If you hadn't gotten involved, the title

14:40.600 --> 14:42.440
of Young Master of Miraculous Craft
would mean nothing.

14:42.440 --> 14:43.670
It wouldn't hurt you at all.

14:43.670 --> 14:45.080
How could it not hurt me?

14:46.480 --> 14:47.270
To you,

14:47.840 --> 14:48.910
the Young Master of Miraculous Craft
is just a title

14:48.910 --> 14:50.770
that can be used to cause trouble.

14:51.080 --> 14:53.270
But for the past 16 years,

14:53.270 --> 14:55.730
it's the only thing
that truly belongs to me.

14:56.630 --> 14:58.090
Not Princess's daughter,

14:58.150 --> 14:59.950
not Grand Tutor Xie's daughter.

15:00.000 --> 15:02.510
It represents me, Xie Jiayu.

15:07.120 --> 15:08.840
To you high and mighty people

15:09.440 --> 15:11.170
who always talk about justice,

15:11.480 --> 15:12.720
it may mean nothing.

15:13.750 --> 15:16.440
You can use and abandon it at will.

15:17.720 --> 15:19.000
But I created it

15:19.000 --> 15:19.790
bit by bit.

15:23.150 --> 15:23.790
And now,

15:24.510 --> 15:26.110
it has been destroyed by you.

15:26.550 --> 15:27.360
And you,

15:27.550 --> 15:28.120
from the beginning to the end,

15:28.120 --> 15:29.520
didn't even ask me a word.

15:32.630 --> 15:33.360
Well, right,

15:34.840 --> 15:35.870
in your eyes,

15:36.440 --> 15:38.510
there are no innocent people
in this world.

15:38.510 --> 15:39.910
For the sake of the world,

15:40.030 --> 15:41.890
you can even sacrifice yourself.

15:43.030 --> 15:44.750
Then what does

15:45.940 --> 15:48.470
my petty unwillingness
amount to, after all?

16:01.840 --> 16:04.040
This is the Shadow-Seeking Butterfly.

16:06.270 --> 16:07.630
I saw the fake Xiao Sheng

16:07.910 --> 16:09.120
in the crowd today,

16:09.720 --> 16:11.920
and that's why I went to the Shenwu Gate.

16:11.960 --> 16:13.690
I didn't mean to ruin your plan.

16:17.190 --> 16:19.120
I sprinkled scented powder on him.

16:19.670 --> 16:21.320
If you send someone to chase him now,

16:21.320 --> 16:22.780
it should still be in time.

16:23.260 --> 16:24.210
If you're lucky,

16:25.120 --> 16:26.450
he might not be dead yet.

16:26.550 --> 16:29.010
You can use him against
the Empress Dowager,

16:29.550 --> 16:30.630
or my father.

16:31.550 --> 16:32.410
Either is fine.

16:40.270 --> 16:42.270
The name
of the Young Master of Miraculous Craft

16:42.270 --> 16:43.400
won't be destroyed.

16:49.240 --> 16:50.440
Dare you come with me?

16:50.670 --> 16:51.270
Where to?

16:52.030 --> 16:53.090
The military camp.

16:54.360 --> 16:55.960
What's there to be afraid of?

17:06.109 --> 17:07.109
Let's play chess.

17:07.880 --> 17:08.589
Master.

17:09.480 --> 17:10.140
Yaoyao said

17:10.240 --> 17:12.270
you had a hand
in those 30,000 fallen souls.

17:12.270 --> 17:13.450
Is it true?

17:13.550 --> 17:14.410
Your Highness.

17:15.720 --> 17:16.720
Let's play chess.

17:23.960 --> 17:26.750
Whether Her Majesty wins or loses tonight,

17:27.589 --> 17:30.400
to you, it's a battle between two rivals

17:31.000 --> 17:32.200
that only benefits a third party.

17:32.200 --> 17:33.600
But I don't want to fight.

17:34.480 --> 17:36.080
I just want Yaoyao to be safe.

17:36.680 --> 17:37.270
Really?

17:37.830 --> 17:38.440
Really.

17:43.480 --> 17:45.830
Before, you were not in power,

17:46.070 --> 17:47.680
so you didn't interfere in politics.

17:47.680 --> 17:50.010
You only needed to live well for yourself.

17:50.480 --> 17:53.610
Now you are only one step away
from the supreme position.

17:53.880 --> 17:55.480
Are you truly not interested

17:55.510 --> 17:57.240
in the game of this world at all?

18:06.110 --> 18:07.570
Your Highness, do you know

18:07.790 --> 18:09.440
that in the current situation,

18:09.440 --> 18:11.510
even the happiness of a simple meal,

18:12.270 --> 18:14.130
without the protection of power,

18:14.680 --> 18:15.310
can be

18:18.920 --> 18:20.400
overturned in an instant?

18:22.240 --> 18:23.110
But only

18:24.200 --> 18:25.440
the chess player

18:26.550 --> 18:28.310
can avoid harm.

18:29.000 --> 18:29.860
Your Highness,

18:32.150 --> 18:35.000
this world is already in your hands,

18:36.160 --> 18:37.440
easily obtainable.

18:38.160 --> 18:39.720
Do you really not want it?

18:53.200 --> 18:54.800
Your Majesty, there is news.

18:55.480 --> 18:56.030
Speak.

18:56.400 --> 18:58.590
Xiao Wuyi refused to hand over
the Young Master of Miraculous Craft.

18:58.590 --> 18:59.750
The soldiers of No. 36 Camp

18:59.750 --> 19:01.110
have already controlled him.

19:01.110 --> 19:03.000
They want to use Xiao Wuyi and Xie Jiayu

19:03.000 --> 19:05.060
to memorialize the fallen soldiers.

19:05.590 --> 19:08.070
Tonight, Prince Jing'an's Mansion
and the Beifu Army

19:08.070 --> 19:10.070
will definitely fight to the death.

19:25.050 --> 19:28.050
[Ziji Palace]

19:31.350 --> 19:33.080
Imperial Guard, hear my order.

19:34.950 --> 19:37.110
Tonight, the Beifu Army's internal strife

19:37.110 --> 19:38.440
will surely lead to a mutiny.

19:38.440 --> 19:40.770
You must seize power at this opportunity.

19:40.960 --> 19:43.310
Whoever seizes
the Beifu Army's official seal

19:43.310 --> 19:44.790
will take the greatest merit.

19:44.790 --> 19:47.110
-Seize the seal, take the greatest merit!
-Seize the seal, take the greatest merit!

19:47.110 --> 19:49.350
-Seize the seal, take the greatest merit!
-Seize the seal, take the greatest merit!

19:49.350 --> 19:54.010
-Seize the seal, take the greatest merit!
-Seize the seal, take the greatest merit!

19:57.680 --> 19:58.640
Her Majesty said

19:59.030 --> 20:01.760
Xiao Wuyi has spent 10 years
in military service,

20:01.830 --> 20:03.720
guarding the borders for Ye.

20:04.030 --> 20:05.760
He should be properly seen off.

20:06.030 --> 20:08.490
The impeachment must be written carefully.

20:08.830 --> 20:10.250
Do not forget his merits,

20:10.440 --> 20:11.920
and do not hide his faults.

20:12.480 --> 20:15.790
Tonight, it is the Beifu Army's
own internal strife.

20:16.550 --> 20:17.680
Do not let people

20:17.680 --> 20:19.960
think that His Majesty and Her Majesty

20:20.110 --> 20:22.170
has wronged him and ruined the world.

20:22.640 --> 20:26.100
-We obey Her Majesty's decree.
-We obey Her Majesty's decree.

20:33.790 --> 20:34.720
What is going on?

20:35.200 --> 20:36.540
Could there be an ambush?

20:36.540 --> 20:37.570
This doesn't look like a mutiny.

20:37.570 --> 20:38.510
Even if they don't revolt,

20:38.510 --> 20:40.170
we must create chaos tonight.

20:40.200 --> 20:41.070
Eunuch He said,

20:41.510 --> 20:43.350
whoever gets
the Beifu Army's official seal

20:43.350 --> 20:44.810
takes the greatest merit!

20:47.620 --> 20:48.920
Oh no, an ambush!

20:49.000 --> 20:49.930
Quick, retreat!

20:54.790 --> 20:55.440
Everyone,

20:56.580 --> 20:57.860
you are a step late.

21:02.180 --> 21:03.620
Arrest them all!

21:11.920 --> 21:13.850
Subject to the Beifu military law,

21:14.310 --> 21:16.240
those who disturb military morale

21:16.440 --> 21:17.500
shall be beheaded;

21:17.590 --> 21:18.960
those who incite mutiny

21:20.480 --> 21:21.540
shall be beheaded.

21:24.000 --> 21:24.750
Fang Shiba,

21:26.270 --> 21:28.680
5 days ago, you left
the camp without permission

21:28.680 --> 21:31.940
and secretly met with
Commander Yue of the Imperial Guard.

21:35.680 --> 21:38.400
I didn't expect Yue Qingyang
to use so little silver

21:38.400 --> 21:41.350
to buy the loyalty and trust
of my Beifu soldiers.

21:42.590 --> 21:43.450
What about you?

21:44.830 --> 21:46.270
Are you all like him?

21:48.400 --> 21:50.000
Disturbing military morale

21:50.350 --> 21:51.350
and rebelling,

21:51.640 --> 21:53.440
according to the law,
you should be cut in half.

21:53.440 --> 21:54.770
There is nothing to say.

21:55.450 --> 21:57.620
I'd say the silver is nothing.

21:58.200 --> 21:59.930
Commander Yue also promised me

22:00.440 --> 22:01.570
that if I succeeded,

22:02.240 --> 22:04.350
he would immediately transfer me
to the Imperial Guard Camp

22:04.350 --> 22:07.350
and transfer my household registration
to Jiankang.

22:07.830 --> 22:09.240
It's better than being a Beifu soldier!

22:09.240 --> 22:09.790
Shut up!

22:10.310 --> 22:11.110
Take him away!

22:11.550 --> 22:12.280
Execute him.

22:12.720 --> 22:15.830
I've long been tired of eating sand
and risking my life in Beifu!

22:15.830 --> 22:17.480
I want to achieve great things!

22:17.480 --> 22:19.440
I want a better life for myself!

22:19.550 --> 22:20.680
Am I wrong?

22:24.200 --> 22:25.060
What about you?

22:26.230 --> 22:27.830
I joined Beifu not for glory,

22:28.110 --> 22:29.240
but for our country.

22:29.640 --> 22:31.110
I don't care about the Imperial Guard.

22:31.110 --> 22:33.110
I also accept military punishment.

22:33.750 --> 22:36.270
But my father and brother
both died in the Battle of Jiuzhang Plain.

22:36.270 --> 22:37.350
I will never let go

22:37.350 --> 22:38.270
of their murderers,

22:38.270 --> 22:39.730
no matter who they are now!

22:40.590 --> 22:41.450
Your Highness,

22:42.140 --> 22:44.070
are you really
going to protect the culprit?

22:44.070 --> 22:44.880
Culprit?

22:46.640 --> 22:47.270
Fine.

22:47.880 --> 22:50.010
Then today, please open your eyes wide

22:50.070 --> 22:51.930
and see if the culprit in your eyes

22:52.790 --> 22:54.200
is truly the culprit.

23:07.580 --> 23:08.720
I am Xie Jiayu.

23:10.000 --> 23:12.830
These are the 18 weapons
I specially forged

23:13.640 --> 23:16.880
to pay tribute to
the 18 fallen Beifu generals.

23:18.270 --> 23:19.350
I planned to offer them

23:19.350 --> 23:20.880
before the Monument of Loyalty
on Double Ninth night.

23:20.880 --> 23:22.550
But last night in front of the monument,

23:22.550 --> 23:24.440
someone used the name
of the Young Master of Miraculous Craft

23:24.440 --> 23:26.240
to sow discord in the Beifu Army.

23:29.720 --> 23:32.070
These are the fragments
of the monument from last night.

23:32.070 --> 23:34.230
This monument was carved
from a plinth stone on the outside,

23:34.230 --> 23:36.630
but the inside
was made of fragile sea rock.

23:36.960 --> 23:38.550
Once exposed to high temperatures,

23:38.550 --> 23:40.550
the inner core of the monument
would burst.

23:40.550 --> 23:42.030
On the Double Ninth Festival,

23:42.030 --> 23:44.680
the monument was surrounded
by lanterns sent by the Empress Dowager.

23:44.680 --> 23:45.880
There were over 100 of them.

23:45.880 --> 23:48.310
Even if what happened last night
had nothing to do with you,

23:48.310 --> 23:50.590
how do you explain the repeating crossbow?

23:50.590 --> 23:52.840
Do you dare say you're not
the Young Master of Miraculous Craft?

23:52.840 --> 23:54.240
Do you dare say the crossbow you designed

23:54.240 --> 23:55.970
didn't end up in the Beifu Army?

24:02.030 --> 24:02.510
Yes.

24:03.480 --> 24:06.210
I am indeed
the Young Master of Miraculous Craft.

24:06.440 --> 24:08.310
I also designed the repeating crossbow.

24:08.310 --> 24:09.510
But I never knew

24:10.160 --> 24:12.290
this crossbow was designed for Beifu.

24:12.550 --> 24:14.720
Oranges thrive south of the Huai River,

24:14.720 --> 24:16.480
yet turn bitter north of it.

24:18.240 --> 24:19.570
Everyone, please look.

24:20.680 --> 24:22.590
Although there are many styles
of the repeating crossbow,

24:22.590 --> 24:24.790
they're all meant for the young masters
of noble families to hunt and play with,

24:24.790 --> 24:26.590
not designed for actual combat.

24:26.640 --> 24:28.310
If it were to be used in actual combat,

24:28.310 --> 24:30.440
the wood would need special treatment

24:30.720 --> 24:31.980
to be flexible enough.

24:32.640 --> 24:35.110
The person who came to me
to buy the blueprint that day

24:35.110 --> 24:36.640
did not tell me its purpose.

24:37.350 --> 24:38.270
I really wonder

24:39.110 --> 24:40.350
how such a repeating crossbow

24:40.350 --> 24:42.480
could actually be sent
to the Northern Border.

24:42.480 --> 24:45.210
If I had known this crossbow
was designed for you,

24:46.920 --> 24:48.650
I would have given you this one.

24:51.110 --> 24:52.350
Although it is not lightweight enough yet,

24:52.350 --> 24:55.010
the range, power, and accuracy
of this crossbow

24:55.400 --> 24:57.660
are what make it fit for the battlefield.

24:57.830 --> 24:58.440
Try it.

25:08.160 --> 25:08.790
This

25:09.350 --> 25:12.550
is the true skill
of the Young Master of Miraculous Craft.

25:15.150 --> 25:17.240
As for the death
of your father and brother,

25:17.240 --> 25:18.100
I am very sorry.

25:18.550 --> 25:20.750
But I can't give you the answer you want,

25:21.110 --> 25:22.640
because I also really want to ask

25:22.640 --> 25:23.200
why such a crossbow,

25:23.200 --> 25:24.920
originally meant for young masters
of noble families to play with,

25:24.920 --> 25:26.550
would be forged in large quantities,

25:26.550 --> 25:28.920
smoothly passed through
the court's strict inspections,

25:28.920 --> 25:30.850
and finally sent to the Beifu Army.

25:31.590 --> 25:34.070
This is not something
the Young Master of Miraculous Craft

25:34.070 --> 25:35.930
and one blueprint could achieve.

25:36.270 --> 25:37.750
The Household Department
makes the weapons.

25:37.750 --> 25:39.280
The problem lies with them.

25:39.720 --> 25:41.520
On his first day back in Jiankang,

25:41.520 --> 25:45.120
His Highness killed
Household Department Adjutant Wei Qianli.

25:49.140 --> 25:51.750
My Beifu soldiers fight for their lives
on the battlefield,

25:51.750 --> 25:54.150
yet the court is full of
useless officials.

25:54.590 --> 25:56.880
Is it enough to just kill
a Household Department Adjutant?

25:56.880 --> 25:58.750
For the innocent souls who died in vain

25:58.750 --> 26:01.110
and for the future safety
of the Northern Border,

26:01.110 --> 26:03.000
it's time to change all this.

26:05.200 --> 26:06.470
Titles based on military merit.

26:06.470 --> 26:07.960
Dismissal of hereditary nobles.

26:07.960 --> 26:09.420
All will start from Beifu.

26:09.880 --> 26:12.400
Please wait for today's court assembly!

26:13.200 --> 26:16.750
-We will obey your orders, Your Highness!
-We will obey your orders, Your Highness!

26:16.750 --> 26:18.550
The death penalty can be spared,

26:18.960 --> 26:20.820
but punishment can't be avoided.

26:22.270 --> 26:23.130
Take them away.

26:23.600 --> 26:25.460
Give them the military flogging!

26:39.670 --> 26:42.580
[Shezhang Hall]

26:46.030 --> 26:46.720
Brother,

26:47.070 --> 26:48.680
who do you think will win today,

26:48.680 --> 26:50.160
the Empress Dowager

26:51.440 --> 26:53.350
or Young Lord Xiao?

26:56.310 --> 26:57.040
I don't know.

26:58.550 --> 27:00.150
If the Empress Dowager wins,

27:02.030 --> 27:03.720
will we be able to leave here?

27:05.430 --> 27:06.670
Or will we die?

27:10.070 --> 27:11.720
Why is it always us

27:12.920 --> 27:14.720
who can't control our own fate

27:15.440 --> 27:17.040
and are at the mercy of others

27:17.640 --> 27:18.790
every single time?

27:47.350 --> 27:48.150
Your Majesty,

27:48.500 --> 27:50.260
I have a matter to report.

27:55.880 --> 27:57.920
Her Majesty is unwell today.

27:58.160 --> 27:59.070
Please report tomorrow.

27:59.070 --> 28:02.200
I want to impeach Xiao Wuyi,
Heir of Prince Jing'an.

28:04.880 --> 28:07.550
I want to impeach Xiao Wuyi,
Heir of Prince Jing'an.

28:07.550 --> 28:11.280
-I also want to impeach Xiao Wuyi.
-I also want to impeach Xiao Wuyi.

28:14.110 --> 28:17.240
My ministers, I've been unwell
these past few days.

28:17.920 --> 28:19.160
If there is no solid proof,

28:19.160 --> 28:21.020
do not cause trouble in the court.

28:22.030 --> 28:22.830
Your Majesty,

28:23.160 --> 28:24.840
all the ministers want to impeach
Young Lord Xiao.

28:24.840 --> 28:26.110
We might as well listen.

28:26.110 --> 28:27.130
If he is truly guilty,

28:27.130 --> 28:29.960
Young Lord Xiao should be punished
by the law of the state right here.

28:29.960 --> 28:31.030
Since you've written them,

28:31.030 --> 28:32.830
what is there that can't be said?

28:32.830 --> 28:34.290
Which of you will go first?

28:36.400 --> 28:37.130
You go first.

28:37.240 --> 28:40.030
I believe Young Lord Xiao
abused his military power,

28:40.030 --> 28:41.160
mobilized troops without authorization,

28:41.160 --> 28:42.110
and deceived his superiors
and subordinates,

28:42.110 --> 28:43.550
leading to a mutiny in the Beifu Army.

28:43.550 --> 28:45.270
I now petition you, Your Majesty,

28:45.270 --> 28:47.400
to strip Xiao Wuyi
of his Beifu Army military seal,

28:47.400 --> 28:48.480
strip him of his rank, imprison him,

28:48.480 --> 28:50.030
and punish him according to his crimes.

28:50.030 --> 28:52.200
I impeach Xiao Wuyi on 29 charges.

28:52.270 --> 28:52.920
First,

28:53.240 --> 28:54.880
he disrupted
the Double Ninth Festival Ceremony,

28:54.880 --> 28:56.270
caused a mutiny in the army,

28:56.270 --> 28:57.400
and disturbed the people.

28:57.400 --> 28:59.750
Second, as the military commander,
Xiao Wuyi

28:59.750 --> 29:01.070
seized his subordinate's widow

29:01.070 --> 29:02.240
and is highly debauched.

29:02.240 --> 29:03.030
Third, Xiao Wuyi—

29:03.030 --> 29:04.750
Are there really that many charges?

29:04.750 --> 29:06.210
It's a long list of crimes,

29:06.310 --> 29:07.640
too numerous to record.

29:08.310 --> 29:09.440
Let me speak for you.

29:09.960 --> 29:12.310
Your Majesty, since I have committed
so many crimes,

29:12.310 --> 29:13.480
I wonder how you

29:13.880 --> 29:15.550
will convict me.

29:15.960 --> 29:16.880
Nonsense.

29:17.070 --> 29:18.750
Young Lord Xiao is a pillar of our Ye.

29:18.750 --> 29:20.610
How can I allow you to slander him?

29:20.640 --> 29:21.720
Untie him at once.

29:22.310 --> 29:23.570
Your Majesty, this...

29:23.680 --> 29:24.810
Hurry and untie him!

29:41.030 --> 29:42.030
Vice Minister Qi,

29:42.640 --> 29:44.880
how did you know about
the mutiny in my Beifu Army?

29:44.880 --> 29:45.720
Who told you?

29:47.270 --> 29:49.530
If you are innocent, why were you tied up?

29:52.110 --> 29:54.680
Last night, a band of bandits
broke into my camp.

29:54.680 --> 29:56.880
They have been captured by the Beifu Army.

29:56.880 --> 29:59.680
Your Majesty, the Beifu Army Camp
is safe and sound,

29:59.680 --> 30:02.010
and can still protect you and His Majesty.

30:02.070 --> 30:04.200
You can rest assured now.

30:04.550 --> 30:06.280
Young Lord Xiao, with you here,

30:06.640 --> 30:07.720
I am at ease.

30:07.790 --> 30:08.640
However,

30:09.400 --> 30:12.310
these bandits
claimed to be from the Imperial Guard,

30:12.310 --> 30:14.310
saying they were ordered
by someone noble in the palace

30:14.310 --> 30:16.510
to instigate a mutiny in the Beifu Army.

30:16.960 --> 30:18.220
By order of the palace?

30:18.550 --> 30:19.790
But I thought...

30:22.720 --> 30:24.240
this was absolutely impossible.

30:24.240 --> 30:25.830
So I killed them all.

30:26.830 --> 30:28.550
I bound myself and came to the court today

30:28.550 --> 30:30.160
just to let you see, Your Majesty,

30:30.160 --> 30:31.640
how many courtiers in the palace

30:31.640 --> 30:33.310
are hoping to make an issue of this.

30:33.310 --> 30:34.270
Now it's great.

30:34.400 --> 30:37.060
All the treacherous ministers
have jumped out.

30:37.750 --> 30:40.200
You did well and right
to kill them, Young Lord Xiao.

30:40.200 --> 30:41.790
The Imperial Guard
guards the imperial city

30:41.790 --> 30:43.790
and forms a bond with the Beifu Army,

30:43.920 --> 30:45.370
together defending Ye.

30:45.440 --> 30:46.240
Your Majesty,

30:46.920 --> 30:49.790
I also have a memorial to present today.

30:50.510 --> 30:51.040
Go ahead.

30:51.310 --> 30:52.440
All the causes today

30:53.510 --> 30:54.720
lie in the military system.

30:54.720 --> 30:56.200
The bows and crossbows
played by young masters of noble families

30:56.200 --> 30:57.920
were sent to the army without inspection,

30:57.920 --> 30:59.510
causing the wrongful deaths
of the troops in Jiuzhang Plain.

30:59.510 --> 31:01.920
Those from poor families
who want to join the Imperial Guard

31:01.920 --> 31:04.400
must first enter noble families
to pass the assessment.

31:04.400 --> 31:05.880
Grain and military provisions
run short every year,

31:05.880 --> 31:07.350
and the pay is in arrears every year.

31:07.350 --> 31:09.960
Even the Imperial Guard, which symbolizes
the royal family's dignity,

31:09.960 --> 31:11.960
can be easily disguised by bandits.

31:12.310 --> 31:14.400
What does all this show?

31:15.830 --> 31:17.480
It shows that the military system
of our dynasty has been deeply flawed

31:17.480 --> 31:18.440
and rotten for a long time.

31:18.440 --> 31:19.680
To cut weeds, you must dig up the roots.

31:19.680 --> 31:20.770
To control water,
you must treat the source.

31:20.770 --> 31:22.960
I've drafted the preliminary proposal
on the "Discourse on Beifu Reform"

31:22.960 --> 31:24.550
and presented it to you, Your Majesty.

31:24.550 --> 31:26.030
Abolish hereditary soldiers,
implement recruitment,

31:26.030 --> 31:27.440
formalize the garrison system,
set up ever-normal granaries,

31:27.440 --> 31:28.920
establish studs, value humble talents,

31:28.920 --> 31:30.240
reduce private troops, and unify commands.

31:30.240 --> 31:31.240
Reform Beifu

31:31.640 --> 31:33.700
to clarify rewards and punishments.

31:36.310 --> 31:38.170
Please approve it, Your Majesty.

31:41.900 --> 31:43.950
[An hour ago]

31:43.510 --> 31:45.840
Who dares to stop Her Majesty's carriage?

31:46.880 --> 31:47.510
Xiao Wuyi?

31:48.920 --> 31:49.400
Didn't you—

31:49.400 --> 31:52.730
Your Majesty, are you waiting for
a mutiny in the Beifu Army?

31:52.750 --> 31:54.280
I'm afraid you won't see it.

32:04.200 --> 32:05.000
Your Majesty,

32:05.160 --> 32:06.820
this is Commander Yue's head!

32:10.160 --> 32:11.350
Xiao Wuyi!

32:11.350 --> 32:15.000
Last night, those from the Imperial Guard
who disrupted my Beifu Army Camp

32:15.000 --> 32:16.790
were all punished
according to military regulations by me.

32:16.790 --> 32:19.590
Now the Beifu Army Camp
is in perfect order.

32:36.750 --> 32:38.480
Her Highness's Shadow-Seeking Butterfly
is really useful,

32:38.480 --> 32:40.440
much more accurate
than the ordinary scented powder

32:40.440 --> 32:42.100
used by the scouts in our army.

32:45.030 --> 32:46.030
Hong Qi,

32:47.440 --> 32:48.770
why aren't you dead yet?

32:48.790 --> 32:51.960
If you don't want
Eunuch Hong to go to the court

32:52.790 --> 32:54.590
and make your actions public...

32:55.110 --> 32:56.070
What do you want?

32:56.350 --> 32:58.790
I ask you to preside over

32:59.960 --> 33:01.070
the Beifu reform.

33:05.240 --> 33:06.400
Your loyalty

33:07.030 --> 33:08.760
can be seen by heaven and earth.

33:09.200 --> 33:11.200
The reform proposal requested by you

33:11.200 --> 33:13.510
is approved for joint discussion
by the Department of State Affairs.

33:13.510 --> 33:14.960
-This...
-This...

33:14.960 --> 33:16.360
Thank you, Your Majesty.

33:20.000 --> 33:21.800
I have another matter to report.

33:22.000 --> 33:23.160
Since the great defeat at Jiuzhang Plain,

33:23.160 --> 33:24.510
the morale of the Northern Qin army
has been greatly frustrated.

33:24.510 --> 33:26.480
The Emperor of Northern Qin wants
to send a delegation for peace talks.

33:26.480 --> 33:28.790
This all relies on His Majesty's prestige
and your benevolence.

33:28.790 --> 33:30.270
Congratulations,

33:30.720 --> 33:31.750
Your Majesty.

33:32.070 --> 33:34.070
Young Lord Xiao, you're too modest.

33:34.070 --> 33:35.960
How would I know about
the war in the Northern Border?

33:35.960 --> 33:37.240
Today's peace

33:37.440 --> 33:38.510
all relies on you

33:38.640 --> 33:41.000
and the Beifu troops
fighting bloody battles.

33:41.000 --> 33:42.360
As for these peace talks,

33:42.360 --> 33:43.620
I'll leave it to you...

33:47.200 --> 33:50.030
and Prince Qi to negotiate together.

33:50.680 --> 33:52.830
You should emulate the diplomatic wisdom
of Lin Xiangru and Lian Po

33:52.830 --> 33:55.310
to show the conciliatory virtue of our Ye.

34:05.890 --> 34:08.500
[Xiyue Restaurant]

34:09.880 --> 34:11.280
A little bit to the right.

34:12.440 --> 34:12.840
Yes.

34:13.960 --> 34:14.620
Right here.

34:17.550 --> 34:18.920
Young Master of Miraculous Craft,

34:18.920 --> 34:20.150
have you finally made up your mind

34:20.150 --> 34:21.949
to spend money to rent this shop?

34:21.960 --> 34:22.440
Yes.

34:22.920 --> 34:24.320
I used to be reluctant to spend money

34:24.320 --> 34:25.550
and always borrowed other people's shops.

34:25.550 --> 34:26.210
From now on,

34:26.630 --> 34:28.840
my own shop is officially open.

34:28.840 --> 34:30.110
-Great!
-Great!

34:31.630 --> 34:33.150
From now on, everyone will know

34:33.150 --> 34:36.110
that I, Xie Jiayu, am
the Young Master of Miraculous Craft.

34:36.110 --> 34:37.960
Young Lord Xiao,
we have to thank you for your help

34:37.960 --> 34:40.440
in officially registering the shop
with the government.

34:40.440 --> 34:41.800
With Beifu as a guarantor,

34:41.800 --> 34:43.440
My Lady, you can openly

34:43.440 --> 34:45.800
research and manufacture weapons
in the future.

34:45.800 --> 34:46.760
He doesn't lose out either.

34:46.760 --> 34:49.489
I also promised to help him
modify the armaments.

34:53.210 --> 34:55.170
[Young Master of Miraculous Craft]

35:03.630 --> 35:04.230
Yue,

35:04.400 --> 35:05.730
may I borrow your sword?

35:16.030 --> 35:18.410
[Miraculous Craft]

35:22.590 --> 35:24.880
From now on, there is only
Miraculous Craft in the world.

35:24.880 --> 35:25.670
I, Xie Jiayu,

35:26.190 --> 35:27.790
even as a woman in this world,

35:28.550 --> 35:30.320
can stand upright and honorable.

35:30.320 --> 35:32.150
-Great!
-Great!

35:32.590 --> 35:32.880
Great!

35:32.880 --> 35:33.940
I think it's great.

35:34.550 --> 35:35.350
I think so too.

35:38.150 --> 35:40.230
Let's go. I'll buy you drinks today.

35:40.230 --> 35:41.030
-Let's go.
-Let's go in.

35:41.030 --> 35:42.400
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

35:43.960 --> 35:45.510
You are included, Xiao Wuyi.

35:45.510 --> 35:49.040
Thank you for allowing me
to clear the name of Miraculous Craft.

35:49.510 --> 35:50.040
Let's go.

36:20.440 --> 36:23.440
I haven't seen the Young Lady
this happy in a long time.

36:23.920 --> 36:27.380
I haven't seen His Highness
this relaxed in a long time either.

36:30.150 --> 36:30.820
This is what happens when you drink.

36:30.820 --> 36:31.590
You are so bad at drinking.

36:31.590 --> 36:33.320
I shouldn't have let you touch a drop.

36:33.320 --> 36:34.030
Nonsense.

36:34.800 --> 36:36.200
I have a great tolerance.

36:36.400 --> 36:37.460
I can drink two Maos

36:39.670 --> 36:40.600
under the table.

36:42.000 --> 36:43.060
What's the number?

36:45.190 --> 36:45.880
Two.

36:46.420 --> 36:47.590
Isn't it two?

36:47.840 --> 36:48.280
Two...

36:51.830 --> 36:53.140
If you really can't walk,

36:53.140 --> 36:54.800
why don't you find a carriage?

36:55.110 --> 36:57.370
You are a lady
of a noble family after all.

36:58.360 --> 37:00.550
I am not a lady of a noble family.

37:01.190 --> 37:03.230
I was taken in by my father and mother.

37:03.230 --> 37:04.430
What did you just say?

37:05.230 --> 37:05.840
Nothing.

37:06.780 --> 37:07.450
Xiao Wuyi,

37:07.840 --> 37:09.130
considering that today,

37:09.130 --> 37:11.790
you helped me save
my title as Miraculous Craft,

37:13.230 --> 37:15.030
I will give you a piece of advice.

37:19.510 --> 37:20.110
Come here.

37:21.550 --> 37:22.750
Come closer, come on.

37:28.710 --> 37:30.670
When it comes to romantic relationships,

37:30.670 --> 37:31.920
it can't be forced.

37:32.670 --> 37:33.280
You

37:34.280 --> 37:35.960
need to be more open-minded.

37:36.920 --> 37:37.590
Look,

37:37.960 --> 37:39.760
Ruisheng and Yuanji

37:39.920 --> 37:41.320
both have someone they like.

37:41.320 --> 37:42.980
You didn't know that, did you?

37:45.960 --> 37:46.560
Forget it.

37:47.030 --> 37:48.710
It's good that you don't know.

37:49.070 --> 37:50.070
I think it's good.

38:01.630 --> 38:02.670
This prayer tablet

38:02.670 --> 38:03.730
is very effective.

38:04.360 --> 38:06.480
It can bless all lovers in the world

38:06.590 --> 38:07.520
will never part.

38:08.070 --> 38:08.840
I saw the other day

38:08.840 --> 38:10.360
that Ruisheng and Yuanji

38:10.360 --> 38:12.000
both inscribed words on their tablets.

38:12.000 --> 38:13.480
Mao and I did it too.

38:18.110 --> 38:19.510
I'll give it to you today.

38:21.030 --> 38:22.760
Let the heavens bless you.

38:24.800 --> 38:25.260
Keep it.

38:29.190 --> 38:30.450
Could it be that you...

38:32.030 --> 38:32.470
Yes.

38:32.840 --> 38:34.550
I saw that the Double Ninth Tree

38:34.550 --> 38:36.350
is full of these prayer tablets.

38:36.880 --> 38:37.810
Very effective.

38:38.320 --> 38:39.070
Try it.

38:39.240 --> 38:40.280
Double Ninth,

38:40.550 --> 38:41.880
for endless longing for those gone before.

38:41.880 --> 38:43.800
The name inscribed on this prayer tablet

38:43.800 --> 38:45.510
foretells either parting in life
or separation by death.

38:45.510 --> 38:46.400
So unlucky.

38:46.710 --> 38:48.710
Never mind, I'd better not tell her.

38:58.030 --> 38:58.960
I'm telling you,

38:59.000 --> 39:01.400
if there is no war in the future,

39:02.150 --> 39:03.800
Mao and I

39:04.030 --> 39:05.290
will travel the world.

39:06.230 --> 39:07.030
That's great.

39:08.190 --> 39:09.320
Where do you want to go?

39:08.520 --> 39:11.250
♪ One glance stirs heart's doom,
near yet far ♪

39:10.670 --> 39:14.000
We'll first go to...

39:11.720 --> 39:14.270
♪ This fleeting moment ♪

39:15.030 --> 39:15.630
Yazhou.

39:16.570 --> 39:20.580
♪ Tugs the threads woven by fate ♪

39:16.670 --> 39:18.870
I heard the sea there is very beautiful.

39:19.630 --> 39:20.800
Then we will go to the northwest.

39:20.750 --> 39:22.750
♪ Bound tight evermore ♪

39:23.150 --> 39:24.480
You have to host us then.

39:24.500 --> 39:27.500
♪ Sharing all the years together ♪

39:26.760 --> 39:27.440
Sure.

39:27.910 --> 39:32.280
♪ Peace I find nowhere but by your side ♪

39:29.280 --> 39:31.010
Then I want the strongest wine.

39:31.590 --> 39:32.870
I'm afraid you won't dare to drink it.

39:32.870 --> 39:35.780
♪ Bear witness with our souls ♪

39:33.400 --> 39:34.150
I dare.

39:36.710 --> 39:39.530
♪ Fear no partings or wax and wane ♪

39:36.760 --> 39:38.290
I definitely dare to drink.

39:39.280 --> 39:39.810
Let's go.

39:40.280 --> 39:43.040
♪ Sincere hearts remain as of old ♪

39:44.280 --> 39:47.400
Your Highness, you want me
to break up Yizhi and your daughter.

39:47.400 --> 39:48.800
But have you ever thought about this?

39:48.800 --> 39:50.330
If it weren't for Prince Qi,

39:50.480 --> 39:51.940
I wouldn't agree so easily

39:51.960 --> 39:53.620
to give Xie Jiayu her freedom.

39:54.150 --> 39:56.590
Even with the Phoenix Heart Token
in your hand,

39:56.590 --> 39:58.440
you wouldn't have that kind of influence.

39:58.440 --> 40:00.590
For those who suffered
hardships in their youth,

40:00.590 --> 40:02.390
survival is the first priority.

40:03.000 --> 40:05.530
Apprenticeships, reputation, and marriage

40:06.230 --> 40:08.290
are all ways to survive in this world.

40:08.320 --> 40:10.450
Prince Qi is not a good match for Jiayu.

40:10.760 --> 40:11.840
Let's make a bet.

40:12.150 --> 40:14.750
Prince Qi will not leave Jiankang
with Yaoyao.

40:19.070 --> 40:20.930
This is what your mother left you.

40:21.480 --> 40:23.150
It is said that this Phoenix Heart Token

40:23.150 --> 40:25.810
contains wealth
that could overturn the world.

40:26.030 --> 40:28.230
The Phoenix Heart Token or Xie Jiayu?

40:29.000 --> 40:31.280
The choice is easy.

40:38.510 --> 40:40.590
I have never believed that a few tokens

40:40.590 --> 40:42.050
could overturn the world.

40:42.440 --> 40:44.110
If you're willing to pledge allegiance
to me with the token,

40:44.110 --> 40:45.110
I will not object.

40:45.110 --> 40:48.110
If you wish to remain silent
as you have for the past 10 years,

40:48.110 --> 40:49.110
that is also fine.

40:49.320 --> 40:51.880
But I will never be coerced.

40:52.630 --> 40:53.490
There is no need

40:54.190 --> 40:55.000
for a deal.

40:59.760 --> 41:00.590
I can help you.

41:04.030 --> 41:06.290
I can help you find the last token holder.

41:07.320 --> 41:09.230
Since you want to fight the noble families

41:09.230 --> 41:10.710
and reform Beifu,

41:11.150 --> 41:12.950
you need all the help you can get.

41:13.190 --> 41:14.790
Since my sister-in-law said

41:15.280 --> 41:18.610
that this Phoenix Heart Token
hides the wealth of the world,

41:18.640 --> 41:20.170
it will certainly help you.

41:24.280 --> 41:26.210
I only want my daughter to be happy.

41:28.280 --> 41:29.280
I can promise you,

41:29.360 --> 41:31.110
but no one can force Xie Jiayu

41:31.440 --> 41:32.900
to go against her own will,

41:33.070 --> 41:34.270
including her father

41:34.710 --> 41:35.630
and Prince Qi.

41:36.760 --> 41:38.760
Xie Jiayu has the freedom to choose.

41:38.760 --> 41:39.620
Including you,

41:41.190 --> 41:42.190
Your Highness.

41:44.030 --> 41:44.710
Naturally.

41:45.510 --> 41:46.310
Including me.

41:47.800 --> 41:48.710
I, Yunzhao,

41:49.190 --> 41:51.230
am willing to serve you, Your Highness,

41:51.230 --> 41:52.440
and find the Phoenix Heart Token.
